1956;;The Indian Fighter;;American;;Andr√© de Toth;;Kirk Douglas, Walter Matthau;;western;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Indian_Fighter;;Johnny Hawks is a man who made his name fighting Indians. Returning to the West after the Civil War he must now keep wronged Sioux warriors from massacring the Oregon-bound wagon train he is leading and the nearby fort. Tensions between the two races are building with Indians trading gold to the whites for whiskey.